- One primary task per delegation; include file paths and references to PROJECT_WORKSPACE.md or Implementation Plan where relevant.
- When delegating, the **response must include the actual slash command(s)** (e.g. `/lead-engineer ...` and `/intern ...`) so the system or user can run them; do not only describe the delegation in text.
